product_name: Keen Maderas Slip-On Shoes - Women's - 2013 Closeout
long_description: A great choice for summer outings thanks to bright colors and breathable cotton canvas uppers, the women's Keen Maderas Slip-On Shoes keep your feet cool and comfortable. Comfortable and breathable cotton canvas uppers offer a natural, easygoing look. Cotton canvas linings are soft against feet. Molded rubber footbeds provide cushioning and comfort for all-day wear. Low-profile, nonmarking rubber outsoles on the Keen Maderas Slip-On Shoes supply good, all-around traction. Closeout.
